text: "I Wonder" is the second single by American singer-songwriter Kellie Pickler. ==Music video== It premiered on VH1 on March 31, 2007. The video debuted at number 19 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of April 26, 2007. It made history on CMT's Top Twenty Countdown for being at number one for consecutive two weeks. ==References== Category:2006 songs Category:Kellie Pickler songs Category:BNA Records singles
title: I Wonder
